TITLE: Setup Node and PNPM Installation Action in GitHub Actions
DESCRIPTION: A reusable GitHub Action for setting up Node.js and installing dependencies using PNPM. This action handles caching to improve workflow efficiency.
SOURCE: https://github.com/obytes/react-native-template-obytes/blob/master/docs/src/content/docs/ci-cd/workflows-references.mdx#2025-04-18_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: yaml
CODE:
```
name: Setup Node & PNPM Install
description: Setup Node.js and install dependencies using PNPM

runs:
  using: composite
  steps:
    - name: Setup Node.js
      uses: actions/setup-node@v3
      with:
        node-version-file: '.nvmrc'
        cache: 'pnpm'

    - name: Install dependencies
      shell: bash
      run: pnpm install
```

